title: MNF recap of Patriots' win & reaction to Mohamed Sanu's trade
itunes:title: MNF recap of Patriots' win & reaction to Mohamed Sanu's trade
description:
DJ and Bucky are back with a new episode. First, the guys recap the Patriots' Monday Night Football win against the Jets and look at how dominant the Patriots' defense has been, while also focusing on Jets' QB Sam Darnold's play (1:11). Next, the pair react to the Patriots' trade for wide receiver Mohamed Sanu and look at how he fits on the team (17:40).
